{"type": "article", "id": 24936, "title": "丰田木块汽车", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-05T07:03:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120308mcsDwVWyZKR4Th60.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是丰田在米兰家具展上展出的木质电动概念车，是用 86 块雪松木板材拼接成的。从正面看它的外壳在车盖和车身上分别是竖条和横条的纹路，颜色有深浅的不规则变化，没有喷漆，很柔和。木块的拼接方式类似于榫卯，不需要使用钉子，设计师希望它能够根据时代变化，当有技术和外形的改变时也能实现替换。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120305WYCnoar3JeTxvZRg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120305mcMDjBIvbwkfVeox.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120306cbHEUYSINk4GtFj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120306Ot0Izwh1pocUFN9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120306uBaQbv4nNX83E2HF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021203076CynoavVTdShQBZl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}